  <li>
    <p>It cannot be denied that, anyhow in the early days, the natural feelings of the family were somewhat outraged by these <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="lightning"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(闪电般的)</code></b> funerals.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Actually the most striking feature of our funerals was their speed. Formalities had been <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="whittled down - (whittle - a large knife)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(逐渐减少/缩减)</code></b>, and, generally speaking, all elaborate ceremonial suppressed.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Next the coffin was loaded on a motor-vehicle—a real <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="hearse"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(灵车)</code></b> or a large converted ambulance. The mourners stepped into one of the few taxis still allowed to <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="to go or travel regularly over, on, or through 这里是运行的意思"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">ply</code></b> and the vehicles drove <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="hell-for-leather - (最早使用是说起码的速度快，leather可能是马鬃)"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(尽快)</code></b> to the cemetery <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="by a route"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(走某条路线)</code></b> avoiding the center of the town.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Let us suppose that these formalities were taking place at the <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="\ ȯg-ˈzil-yə-rē \ 备用的/附加的 functioning in a subsidiary capacity"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">auxiliary</code></b> hospital of which Dr. Rieux was in charge. This converted school had an exit at the back of the main building. A large storeroom <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="giving on"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(朝向/面向)</code></b> the corridor contained the coffins.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>In lifeless squares and avenues these <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="\ ˈtȯ-drē , ˈtä- \ cheap and gaudy in appearance or quality 廉价而又俗丽的"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">tawdry</code></b> idols <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="lorded it"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(对...作威作福，这里理解为高高居于宝座之上)</code></b> under the lowering sky; stolid monsters that might have <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="象征着"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">personified</code></b> the rule of immobility imposed on us.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Indeed, had not the epidemic, as already mentioned, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="spread its ravages"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(延伸破坏性)</code></b>, <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="all would have been for the best"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(一切都会很好)</code></b>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>The ambulance had already left and was being sprayed with disinfectant, and while spadefuls of clay thudded more and more dully on the rising layer of earth, the family were <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="bundling into"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(挤进[某个空间])</code></b> the taxi.</p>
  </li>
